==English==

===Noun===
'''napalm'''

# {{uncountable}} A [[highly]] [[inflammable]], [[viscous]] [[substance]], (designed to [[stick]] to the body while [[burn]]ing), used in [[warfare]] to cause widespread [[death]] and [[destruction]], especially in [[wooded]] areas.

===Verb===
'''napalm'''

# {{transitive}} To [[spray]] or [[attack]] an [[area]] using such substance.

